{"tid":1131431,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"Router路由器 集中討論區(13)","createTime":"2019-04-29T15:51:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-29T16:32:20.000Z","uid":9050,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"15a9401fa42307b1166c10d246dfe0dea2647d79","tid":1131431,"uid":9050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T15:51:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>常見用語</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><ins>Mesh WiFi</ins></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n由兩個或以上嘅Mesh point組成，可以擴大WiFi嘅覆蓋範圍。<br />\n佢同傳統嘅WiFi extender/repeater之間最大嘅分別係，Repeater本質上係Device嚟，而Mesh Point你可以視佢為Router嘅一部分。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/01/005942_3f42e60c75c4429de821e0eca32ebcd3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F01%2F005942_3f42e60c75c4429de821e0eca32ebcd3.jpg&h=49a15172&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nMesh point之間有獨立嘅channel連結，相比於Repeater只係將佢接收到嘅WiFi signal再發射出去，Mesh WiFi可以減低速度嘅衰弱。而且Mesh WiFi會組成一個SSID network，姐係當你由房行出廳再行出花園嘅時候佢會自動選擇最適合嘅WiFi point，而唔使好似於Repeater咁要手動轉WiFi。<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><ins>MU-MIMO</ins></strong></span><br />\n<br />\nMulti-User Multiple-Input Multiple-Output，顧名思義係處理同時間連接多個Device嘅技術。背後嘅原理非常複雜，有興趣嘅可以自己上Google睇。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/01/010059_a0a81712a76bbca995ad0e46b9951337.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F01%2F010059_a0a81712a76bbca995ad0e46b9951337.jpg&h=0a31fc0e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大概嚟講，以往嘅Router會逐個逐個device輪流去處理，而呢個shifting係需要時間去處理。假如有4部可以行到100Mbps電話連接左你部Router，由於喺一秒鐘入面，每部電話只有四分之一嘅時間可以同Router溝通，所以每部電話都得返1/4姐係25Mbps嘅速度。而MU-MIMO技術就透過魔法，做到好多條互相獨立嘅connection出嚟，每個Device都可以用盡自己嘅資源。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><ins>Home Plug</ins></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n係Digital嘅世界，有Frequency就有Signal。所有燈可以傳送訊號、聲音可以傳送訊號，AC電線自然都可以用嚟傳送訊號。HomePlug就係可以利用一組插落三腳插嘅裝置互相連接，好處係可以無視牆嘅存在，有電制就上到網。壤處亦都好明顯，如果你間屋有咁上下樓齡，電線開始老化，HomePlug嘅速度亦都會大幅下降。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/01/010121_7e10378bf6ce30068d78437efca2b1f7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F01%2F010121_7e10378bf6ce30068d78437efca2b1f7.jpg&h=44a720d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<ins><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">一般問題</span></ins><br />\n<br />\nQ1: 想知道天線係咪越大支越大dBi越好？<br />\nA1: 大家冷靜D 睇左圖先。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁以下圖睇解釋左，天線訊號係似甜圈圈，越高dBi支只係會遠但扁，反之近但闊。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/25/125743_a6cab5a0e57609a58bd9b58fa71ab6b3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F25%2F125743_a6cab5a0e57609a58bd9b58fa71ab6b3.png&h=305da2a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/25/125744_4b3981b72136081f3bb6259d6e796c23.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F25%2F125744_4b3981b72136081f3bb6259d6e796c23.jpg&h=1ce39ccb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nQ2: 想知個天線一支支點樣SETUP好呀?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nA2: 以甜圈圈效應，單層戶，全向上即可( I I I I )；雙層或以上就跟圖 ( \\ I I / ) 得到全面覆蓋。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/25/125803_e366dff37d9182692b84bbf533ffc504.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F25%2F125803_e366dff37d9182692b84bbf533ffc504.png&h=d0a28a7a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nQ3: 2.4G 好慢有無設定建議?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nA3: 有既，可以set死20MHz+頻道1/6/11，唔好set 40MHz，會干擾得好勁(原理如下圖)，但香港咁高密度，都係用返5G喇。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/25/125832_38f16c4ff1182b0f1961907b7effd27c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F25%2F125832_38f16c4ff1182b0f1961907b7effd27c.png&h=df4ea856&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nQ4: 咁5G設定呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nA4: Set死80MHz + 頻道3位數自選就ok。現時勿揀160MHz<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nQ5: 有無實用網站參考呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nA5: 睇睇以下資料網<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.smallnetbuilder.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.smallnetbuilder.com&d=exB9%2BbP5di4RF4u3Oz7pYspe%2FvQB%2B59L3xQItPRvby0%3D&h=c2a9c81c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.smallnetbuilder.com</a> Router測試/評測網<br />\n<a href=\"https://wikidevi.com/wiki/Main_Page\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwikidevi.com%2Fwiki%2FMain_Page&d=exB9%2BbP5di4RF4u3Oz7pYspe%2FvQB%2B59L3xQItPRvby0%3D&h=b0ca95ed\" target=\"_blank\">https://wikidevi.com/wiki/Main_Page</a> Router版Wiki<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.duckware.com/tech/wifi-in-the-us.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.duckware.com%2Ftech%2Fwifi-in-the-us.html&d=exB9%2BbP5di4RF4u3Oz7pYspe%2FvQB%2B59L3xQItPRvby0%3D&h=37705491\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.duckware.com/tech/wifi-in-the-us.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nQ6: 想問下MB/s同Mb/s點換算？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nA6: 1MB/s = 8 Mb/s<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nQ7: 用左1000m又買左勁router，點解我Device收得咁慢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nA7: Device上下載速度受天線數量影響，理論值上限數據如下:<br />\nExample: On a single 80 Mhz 802.11ac channel operating at 433 Mbps<br />\nAll on the same 80 Mhz channel<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n1&times;1 433 Mbps<br />\n2&times;2 866 Mbps<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />多數Device都係雙天線<br />\n3&times;3 1300 Mbps<br />\n4&times;4 1733 Mbps <br />\n8&times;8 3466 Mbps<br />\n理論值扣返一半就係現實值<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nQ8: 有無Router推薦下<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/ok.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nA8: 咁預設大家都用500M/1000M<br />\n首先問自己牌子係咪<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>TP-Link或支那牌子</strong></span></span><br />\n係既就唔洗再討論落去<br />\n推薦list睇budget做人<br />\n少過$600是但買就得<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">方形屋：</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />單Router用家<br />\n&lt;$800: AC66U B1 / AC58U / EA6350v3<br />\n$800-900: R7000 / AC68U / EA7500v2<br />\n$1000+: R7800 / AC86U / EA8300<br />\n$1500+: AC88u / EA9300<br />\n$2000+: GT5300 / EA9500s<br />\n$3000+(AX系列 - s10用家適用): AX88u / AX8<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />Mesh用家<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">雙頻</span>mesh wifi (平玩之選) - 範圍大但唔多機用<br />\n(雙機mesh) <br />\n&lt;$1200: Velop ac2600 <br />\n<br />\n(三機mesh)<br />\n&lt;$1600: Velop ac3900<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">長形/奇怪形：</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> Mesh用家<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">三頻</span>mesh wifi - 範圍大又多機連接<br />\n(雙機mesh) <br />\n&lt;$2000: RBK20 / Velop ac4400<br />\n$2000-2500: RBK40<br />\n$3000: RBK50<br />\n<br />\n(三機mesh)<br />\n$2700: RBK23 / Velop ac6600<br />\n$3100: RBK43<br />\n$4400: RBK53<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">ASUS Aimesh: (擴充/入門之選)</span><br />\n適用於以下機型：<br />\nRT-AC66U B1<br />\nLyra Trio<br />\nAC68U<br />\nAC2200 Lyra <br />\nBlue Cave<br />\nRT-AC86U<br />\nAC3100 RT-AC88U<br />\nRT-AC5300 <br />\nROG Rapture GT-AC5300<br />\nRT-AX88U<br />\nROG Rapture GT-AX11000<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n請勿使用支那品牌Router<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n請勿使用支那品牌Router<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n請勿使用支那品牌Router<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好重要 要講3次<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Big Brother is WATCHING YOU!!!</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">小弟都係新手，志在對Router有興趣同大家討論下，有待各巴打補完。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"3af7215db7e44dd9499a1a904824cc374be8096a","tid":1131431,"uid":18947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T16:16:06.000Z","msg":"咁快？"},{"pid":"65c456f3649a0faf58b1cfba58591b230e3bb64f","tid":1131431,"uid":9050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3af7215db7e44dd9499a1a904824cc374be8096a","tid":1131431,"uid":18947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T16:16:06.000Z","msg":"咁快？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T16:19:30.000Z","msg":"驚聽日爆post<br />\n但內容有修正就修正左先<br />\n電話好難改野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbded5600cb31501af654e3078c0ca5a1fbe334c","tid":1131431,"uid":18947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"65c456f3649a0faf58b1cfba58591b230e3bb64f","tid":1131431,"uid":9050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3af7215db7e44dd9499a1a904824cc374be8096a","tid":1131431,"uid":18947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T16:16:06.000Z","msg":"咁快？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T16:19:30.000Z","msg":"驚聽日爆post<br />\n但內容有修正就修正左先<br />\n電話好難改野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T16:22:55.000Z","msg":"無up到我張圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 等我仲畫得咁辛苦"},{"pid":"faf65ce5fa2bb841bf1b9a68e6894bd707e9d39b","tid":1131431,"uid":2129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T16:31:24.000Z","msg":"新po留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efb8f2f1e18147920c280f1e6de694b4d104d7c2","tid":1131431,"uid":9050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T16:32:20.000Z","msg":"唔好意思<br />\n大家請移玉步向修正版<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nRouter路由器 集中討論區(13)修正版<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1131496\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1131496</a>"}]}